Join @punk4156, @metaverseDAO and @AccelerateArt for the inaugural exhibition of work from the esteemed 4156 collection. Featuring a live tour of the 4156 Crypovoxels exhibition, 11 new ape-themed portraits that are to be auctioned on OpenSea.
